elements.title: massacre of 257 inhabitants of a Polish village
elements.contents: ... that during World War II, a Polish priest and a German officer could not prevent the massacre of 257 inhabitants of a Polish village (commemoration pictured)?

elements.title: being rivals since 1977

elements.title: Wrap Me Up
